title: Signature
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Written as $$\Sigma$$

Contains elements $$(f,n)$$ with $$F$$ being a function an $$n$$ being its arity

For example [[Peano Arithmetic]]  signature: $$\Sigma_{PA} = \{ (0,0), (a,2), (m,2), (s,1) \}$$
